defaultThe Council believes that understanding it’s expenditure and the markets in which it operates is a continual and on-going process. The Council has a growing understanding of its expenditure and is implementing system developments to enhance the quality and granularity of its data. The Council is also developing its general market knowledge and awareness through the transition to a Category Management approach.
