defaultWhat Can be Done To Improvedefault&#xa0;
defaultThe main difficulty the Council faces is in keeping abreast of the market developments taking place across the wider public sector. There is an opportunity for central gathering and dissemination (via some form of market intelligence portal possibly) of market developments (new entrants to markets, key leavers from markets, new models of delivery etc.) that local Category Managers can access easily and efficiently.
